eyed, respectively, by the sound of the speaker. Tone seems like a continuation of intonation in this way. In considering how languages develop, I wonder whether intonation progressed into tone systems in tonal languages, intonation developed from tone, or if the two progressed independently of each other.%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
